### PoPunkouterSoftware — API Tests
### Run these with the REST Client extension (Ctrl+Alt+R) or JetBrains HTTP Client
### Server must be running on http://localhost:5000

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

# ─── Health ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/health — probe all external connections
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── Config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/config — client uses this to discover API base URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/config
Accept: application/json

###

# ─── Azure Report ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /api/diag/report — load latest Azure report (Table Storage then file fallback)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/report
Accept: application/json

###

### POST /api/diag/refresh — trigger live Azure SDK refresh (takes 30–90 seconds)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/diag/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

# ─── OpenAPI / Scalar ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET /openapi/v1.json — raw OpenAPI spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Scalar UI (open in browser)
# http://localhost:5000/scalar

